THE HEADLESS RIDER WHO--

00:02:38.613 --> 00:02:39.980
&gt;&gt; THE U.S. HAS ALREADY MADE

00:02:39.980 --> 00:02:41.648
CONTACT WITH THE HEADLESS RIDER

