00:03:22.917 --> 00:03:24.819
LEAD TO TRUE LOVE.

00:03:24.819 --> 00:03:26.787
&gt;&gt; I AM SO IN LOVE WITH YOU,

00:03:26.787 --> 00:03:27.655
SEIJI.

00:03:27.655 --> 00:03:29.322
