00:03:35.862 --> 00:03:36.729
JEALOUS.

00:03:36.729 --> 00:03:38.130
&gt;&gt; THEN DON’T LOOK AT THEM.

00:03:38.130 --> 00:03:39.765
&gt;&gt; DUDE, IF A CHICK’S HOT, YOU

00:03:39.765 --> 00:03:40.732
LOOK AT HER, AND THEN YOU GO

00:03:40.732 --> 00:03:41.700
TALK TO HER.

00:03:41.700 --> 00:03:42.834
THESE THINGS ARE CARVED

00:03:42.834 --> 00:03:43.835
IN OUR DNA.

00:03:43.835 --> 00:03:44.903
IT’S THE BRO SHOW, DUDE.

00:03:44.903 --> 00:03:46.037
IT’S WHAT WE DO!

00:03:46.037 --> 00:03:47.105
&gt;&gt; YEAH, I DON’T WANT TO BE

00:03:47.105 --> 00:03:48.273
ON THAT SHOW.

00:03:48.273 --> 00:03:50.174
&gt;&gt; NO NEED TO WORRY, MY LOVE.

00:03:50.174 --> 00:03:52.076
THIS BODY MAY BELONG TO GIRLS

00:03:52.076 --> 00:03:54.078
EVERYWHERE, BUT MY HEART IS ALL

00:03:54.078 --> 00:03:55.045
YOURS, ANRI.

00:03:55.045 --> 00:03:56.146
YOU KNOW WHAT I ALWAYS ASK

00:03:56.146 --> 00:03:56.946
MYSELF?

00:03:56.946 --> 00:03:58.782
WHY IS ANRI SO BOOBIE-LICIOUS,

00:03:58.782 --> 00:03:59.849
SO SEXY-CUTE?

00:03:59.849 --> 00:04:01.684
