00:04:10.292 --> 00:04:11.359
&gt;&gt; WELL, I--

00:04:11.359 --> 00:04:13.194
&gt;&gt; OH, ARE YOU SAYING THAT YOU

00:04:13.194 --> 00:04:14.361
DON’T THINK THAT SHE’S CUTE?

00:04:14.361 --> 00:04:15.196
&gt;&gt; NO!

00:04:15.196 --> 00:04:16.063
I MEAN, YES.

00:04:16.063 --> 00:04:20.333
I DO THINK SHE’S CU--[muffled]

00:04:20.333 --> 00:04:21.201
&gt;&gt; GOT IT.

00:04:21.201 --> 00:04:22.803
SO YOU ADMIT, SHE’S DEFINITELY

00:04:22.803 --> 00:04:23.369
CUTE.

00:04:23.369 --> 00:04:25.037
BUT I’M WILLING TO ADMIT SHE’S

00:04:25.037 --> 00:04:26.639
BOOBIE-LICIOUS, THUS

00:04:26.639 --> 00:04:27.707
EXHIBITING THAT MY LOVE FOR

00:04:27.707 --> 00:04:29.709
THIS FINE CHICK GOES WAY

00:04:29.709 --> 00:04:31.076
DEEPER THAN YOURS.

00:04:31.076 --> 00:04:33.678
WHICH MEANS, I WIN, YOU LOSE!

00:04:33.678 --> 00:04:34.879
&gt;&gt; WHAT KIND OF SELF-CENTERED

00:04:34.879 --> 00:04:36.014
LOGIC IS THAT?

00:04:36.014 --> 00:04:38.849
&gt;&gt; LOSER!

00:04:38.849 --> 00:04:40.351
&gt;&gt; SIX MONTHS AGO, THERE WAS A

00:04:40.351 --> 00:04:41.919
LITTLE BIT OF AN INCIDENT.

00:04:41.919 --> 00:04:43.353
AND FOR A WHILE IT SEEMED

00:04:43.353 --> 00:04:44.754
LIKED THE WHOLE SCHOOL, THE

00:04:44.754 --> 00:04:50.226
WHOLE CITY WAS TAKING ABOUT IT.

00:04:50.226 --> 00:04:52.028
BUT THAT SAID, IT HAD

00:04:52.028 --> 00:04:53.729
NOTHING TO DO WITH HER,

00:04:53.729 --> 00:04:57.065
SO SHE WASN’T INTERESTED.

00:04:58.867 --> 00:05:00.835
&gt;&gt; [chuckles]

00:05:04.805 --> 00:05:05.840
&gt;&gt; [laughs]

00:05:05.840 --> 00:05:07.074
&gt;&gt; [grunts]

00:05:09.209 --> 00:05:11.377
&gt;&gt; YOU OKAY?

00:05:11.377 --> 00:05:12.411
&gt;&gt; YEAH.

00:05:12.411 --> 00:05:13.847
I’M FINE, THANKS.

00:05:13.847 --> 00:05:16.115
NOTHING HAPPENS.

00:05:16.115 --> 00:05:17.850
NOTHING CHANGES.

00:05:17.850 --> 00:05:21.186
AND THAT WAS HER DAILY LIFE.

00:05:21.186 --> 00:05:24.856
[sinister laughter]

