&gt;&gt; HURRYING.

00:05:32.996 --> 00:05:33.864
WHAT’RE YOU GONNA DO

00:05:33.864 --> 00:05:35.098
WITH THAT POSTER, YUMACH?

00:05:35.098 --> 00:05:37.433
[sinister laughter]

00:05:37.433 --> 00:05:38.834
&gt;&gt; SHE’S SURE IN A HURRY.

00:05:38.834 --> 00:05:39.935
&gt;&gt; WHAT DO YOU THINK?

00:05:39.935 --> 00:05:41.103
SHE’S GETTING A LITTLE MORE

00:05:41.103 --> 00:05:43.472
BRAZEN IN BROAD DAYLIGHT LATELY.

00:05:43.472 --> 00:05:45.274
&gt;&gt; YEAH, I AGREE.

00:05:50.878 --> 00:05:52.012
&gt;&gt; YOU KNOW, I PREFER IT WHEN

00:05:52.012 --> 00:05:53.281
THE SPOOKY STUFF LURKS IN THE

00:05:53.281 --> 00:05:55.015
SHADOWS LIKE IT’S SUPPOSED TO.

