LIKE, "THE LADY’S

00:05:59.086 --> 00:06:00.086
PRIVATE AFFAIRS"?

00:06:00.086 --> 00:06:01.354
&gt;&gt; YEAH, THE SECRET OF

00:06:01.354 --> 00:06:02.755
HARUKA NOGIZAKA.

00:06:02.755 --> 00:06:03.890
&gt;&gt; JUST SHUT IT.

00:06:03.890 --> 00:06:04.957
&gt;&gt; IT’S ALL GOOD.

00:06:04.957 --> 00:06:07.826
SHE’S GOT HER REASONS, I’M SURE.

00:06:07.826 --> 00:06:09.360
LEAVE HER BE.

