STUPIDITY WORKS LIKE A

00:10:54.473 --> 00:10:55.741
PROTECTIVE FILTER.

00:10:55.741 --> 00:10:58.276
&gt;&gt; YO, THIS DUDE’S NUTTIER THAN

00:10:58.276 --> 00:10:59.444
A SQUIRREL TURD.

00:10:59.444 --> 00:11:00.611
&gt;&gt; YEAH, BUT HE’S FREE

00:11:00.611 --> 00:11:01.512
ENTERTAINMENT.

00:11:01.512 --> 00:11:04.515
[laughs]

00:11:04.515 --> 00:11:07.284
[all laugh]

00:11:07.284 --> 00:11:08.652
&gt;&gt; [laughs]

00:11:08.652 --> 00:11:10.587
ALL RIGHT, IT’S TIME TO SHOW

00:11:10.587 --> 00:11:13.089
YOU BOYS WHAT GROWN-UPS CAN DO.

00:11:13.089 --> 00:11:14.591
THANKS TO THE PROTECTIONS YOU

00:11:14.591 --> 00:11:16.559
RECEIVE UNDER THE JUVENILE LAW,

00:11:16.559 --> 00:11:17.993
