FREE TO HARASS OR EVEN KILL ANY

00:11:20.195 --> 00:11:21.764
POOR SOUL YOU CHOOSE.

00:11:21.764 --> 00:11:23.565
BUT ALWAYS KEEP IN MIND,

00:11:23.565 --> 00:11:24.766
WHEN YOU SET OUT TO KILL A

00:11:24.766 --> 00:11:26.634
PERSON, YOU MUST BE PREPARED

00:11:26.634 --> 00:11:27.769
FOR THAT PERSON TO HAVE THE

00:11:27.769 --> 00:11:29.236
WHEREWITHAL--

00:11:29.236 --> 00:11:30.537
&gt;&gt; YOU’RE FREAKIN’ WHACKED,

00:11:30.537 --> 00:11:31.405
OLD MAN.

00:11:31.405 --> 00:11:32.539
&gt;&gt; [groans]

00:11:32.539 --> 00:11:34.007
&gt;&gt; AND GUESS WHAT, GRAMPS?

00:11:34.007 --> 00:11:35.442
I’M OVER 20.

00:11:35.442 --> 00:11:36.743
&gt;&gt; [groans]

