THAT REALLY HURTS!

00:11:39.345 --> 00:11:40.613
AND I CAN’T RUN AWAY WITH YOU

00:11:40.613 --> 00:11:41.781
STEPPING ON MY FOOT!

00:11:41.781 --> 00:11:43.115
[groans]

00:11:43.115 --> 00:11:44.116
OOH, THAT FINGER IS REALLY

00:11:44.116 --> 00:11:44.583
SHARP.

00:11:44.583 --> 00:11:47.086
OW! IT’S POKING, IT’S POKING!

00:11:47.086 --> 00:11:48.186
WHY ARE YOU JUST STANDING

00:11:48.186 --> 00:11:48.653
THERE, CELTY?

00:11:48.653 --> 00:11:49.554
&gt;&gt; HUH?

00:11:49.554 --> 00:11:50.454
&gt;&gt; WILL YOU HURRY UP AND SAVE

00:11:50.454 --> 00:11:51.455
ME?

00:11:51.455 --> 00:11:52.590
[confused reactions]

00:11:54.592 --> 00:11:57.595
&gt;&gt; I REALLY DON’T WANT TO.

00:11:57.595 --> 00:11:58.595
&gt;&gt; COULDN’T YOU SEE

00:11:58.595 --> 00:11:59.529
I WAS MOUTHING-OFF TO THESE

00:11:59.529 --> 00:12:01.664
HOOLIGANS JUST ’CAUSE I SAW YOU

00:12:01.664 --> 00:12:03.099
THERE, WHICH GAVE ME A FALSE

00:12:03.099 --> 00:12:06.702
SENSE OF BRAVADO?

00:12:06.702 --> 00:12:08.437
&gt;&gt; HORADA, TAKE A LOOK.

00:12:08.437 --> 00:12:09.171
CHECK IT OUT.

00:12:09.171 --> 00:12:10.306
IT’S THE BLACK RIDER.

00:12:10.306 --> 00:12:10.806
&gt;&gt; WHAT?

00:12:10.806 --> 00:12:12.407
DON’T BE JACKIN’ WITH ME.

00:12:12.407 --> 00:12:13.241
&gt;&gt; YEAH, MAN.

00:12:13.241 --> 00:12:15.176
I TOTALLY SAW IT ON THE TV.

00:12:17.645 --> 00:12:18.679
&gt;&gt; [grunts]

00:12:18.679 --> 00:12:20.480
[phone clatters]

00:12:20.480 --> 00:12:21.348
I HEARD YOU MADE AN

00:12:21.348 --> 00:12:22.649
APPEARANCE AT THAT BIG DOLLARS

00:12:22.649 --> 00:12:23.550
MEETING THAT TOOK PLACE

00:12:23.550 --> 00:12:24.718
SIX MONTHS AGO.

00:12:24.718 --> 00:12:25.652
[groans]

00:12:25.652 --> 00:12:27.286
I’M TIRED OF PEOPLE SHOWING UP

00:12:27.286 --> 00:12:28.354
AND ACTING ALL TOUGH IN OUR

00:12:28.354 --> 00:12:29.188
TERRITORY.

00:12:29.188 --> 00:12:30.256
COME ON!

00:12:30.256 --> 00:12:32.057
YOU GOT SOMETHIN’ TO SAY?

00:12:32.057 --> 00:12:33.726
HUH?

00:12:33.726 --> 00:12:36.094
[mockingly] HUH?

00:12:43.200 --> 00:12:45.602
&gt;&gt; WHAT’S TH--?

00:12:45.602 --> 00:12:49.172
[panicked reaction]

00:12:49.172 --> 00:12:50.406
&gt;&gt; HUH?

00:12:53.543 --> 00:12:55.545
WHAT THE HELL IS THIS?

00:12:55.545 --> 00:12:58.380
[frightened reactions]

00:12:58.380 --> 00:13:00.215
HEY, WAIT!

00:13:00.215 --> 00:13:02.250
[screams]

00:13:04.753 --> 00:13:06.087
&gt;&gt; HMM.

00:13:06.087 --> 00:13:07.755
NOW THAT WAS THE PROPER

00:13:07.755 --> 00:13:09.790
REACTION.

00:13:14.561 --> 00:13:15.862
OH, GOOD.

00:13:15.862 --> 00:13:17.496
IT’S NOT BROKEN.

00:13:17.496 --> 00:13:19.765
SHINRA GAVE THIS TO ME.

00:13:19.765 --> 00:13:21.133
&gt;&gt; [laughs]

00:13:21.133 --> 00:13:22.234
TAKE THAT!

00:13:22.234 --> 00:13:23.769
NOW YOU’VE SEEN THE POWER OF

00:13:23.769 --> 00:13:24.503
THE GROWN-UPS!
[laughs]

00:13:27.238 --> 00:13:29.440
&gt;&gt; I REALLY DON’T LIKE HIM.

00:13:50.625 --> 00:13:51.859
&gt;&gt; JEEZ.

00:13:51.859 --> 00:13:54.428
IS THERE REALLY A POINT TO THIS?

00:14:05.605 --> 00:14:07.306
HOW DO YOU PLAY THIS GAME

00:14:07.306 --> 00:14:08.908
ANYWAY?

00:14:08.908 --> 00:14:11.210
&gt;&gt; RUSSIA SUSHI GOOD!

00:14:11.210 --> 00:14:12.511
RUSSIA SUSHI CHEAP!

00:14:12.511 --> 00:14:13.645
FOR YOU, BIG SPENDER.

00:14:13.645 --> 00:14:14.913
OH, IZAYA!

00:14:14.913 --> 00:14:16.414
&gt;&gt; WELL, NOW, I SEE THAT

00:14:16.414 --> 00:14:17.781
YOU’RE WORKING HARD AS EVER.

00:14:17.781 --> 00:14:19.683
&gt;&gt; YOU COME TO IKEBUKURO LOTS

00:14:19.683 --> 00:14:20.518
LATELY.

00:14:20.518 --> 00:14:21.752
YOU STOP BY RESTAURANT AND EAT

00:14:21.752 --> 00:14:22.486
GOOD.

00:14:22.486 --> 00:14:24.321
SEE TODAY, WE JUST OPEN BRAND

00:14:24.321 --> 00:14:25.222
NEW CAN.

00:14:25.222 --> 00:14:26.723
FISH VERY FRESH!

00:14:26.723 --> 00:14:28.725
&gt;&gt; I’D LOVE TO, BUT I’M A LITTLE

00:14:28.725 --> 00:14:29.826
BUSY TODAY.

00:14:29.826 --> 00:14:33.395
I’LL STOP BY SOON, THOUGH.

00:14:33.395 --> 00:14:35.797
&gt;&gt; HEY.

00:14:35.797 --> 00:14:38.266
[speaking Russian]

00:14:38.266 --> 00:14:41.869
&gt;&gt; [speaking Russian]

00:14:41.869 --> 00:14:43.904
THAT RIGHT?

00:14:48.475 --> 00:14:49.543
&gt;&gt; LET’S SEE WHO KNOWS

00:14:49.543 --> 00:14:51.410
ANRI BETTER--MIKADO OR ME.

00:14:51.410 --> 00:14:52.545
WE’LL START BY LISTING ALL THE

00:14:52.545 --> 00:14:54.480
GOOD TRAITS WE THINK SHE HAS.

00:14:54.480 --> 00:14:55.614
ME FIRST.

00:14:55.614 --> 00:14:56.782
BOOBIE-LICIOUS!

00:14:56.782 --> 00:14:57.750
&gt;&gt; THAT’S WHERE YOU START?

00:14:57.750 --> 00:14:58.884
CAN YOU TRY AND STAY AWAY

00:14:58.884 --> 00:15:00.218
FROM USING THAT WORD?

00:15:00.218 --> 00:15:01.353
&gt;&gt; LIVE BY THE BOOBIE,

00:15:01.353 --> 00:15:02.687
DIE BY THE BOOBIE.

00:15:02.687 --> 00:15:04.356
&gt;&gt; WHAT DOES THAT EVEN MEAN?

00:15:04.356 --> 00:15:05.490
&gt;&gt; THIS WAS THE FIRST TIME IN

00:15:05.490 --> 00:15:06.758
HER LIFE THAT SHE’D EVER HAD

00:15:06.758 --> 00:15:07.925
GUY FRIENDS.

00:15:07.925 --> 00:15:10.194
ACTUALLY, THIS IS PROBABLY

00:15:10.194 --> 00:15:11.762
THE FIRST TIME THAT SHE’S TRULY

00:15:11.762 --> 00:15:13.229
BEEN FRIENDS WITH ANYONE.

00:15:13.229 --> 00:15:13.964
&gt;&gt; I WOULD IF YOU’D GIVE ME

00:15:13.964 --> 00:15:14.731
A SECOND!

00:15:14.731 --> 00:15:16.566
&gt;&gt; OKAY, THEN SAY IT.

00:15:16.566 --> 00:15:17.567
I’M WAITING.

00:15:17.567 --> 00:15:18.701
&gt;&gt; WELL, I THINK--

00:15:18.701 --> 00:15:19.702
&gt;&gt; HER ROLE USED TO BE MAKING

00:15:19.702 --> 00:15:21.270
MIKA HARIMA LOOK LIKE THE MORE

00:15:21.270 --> 00:15:22.737
ATTRACTIVE ONE IN THE GROUP.

00:15:22.737 --> 00:15:24.773
AND SHE WAS FINE WITH THAT.

00:15:24.773 --> 00:15:26.608
SHE KNEW WHAT ROLE TO PLAY

00:15:26.608 --> 00:15:27.709
WITH HER.

00:15:27.709 --> 00:15:30.878
BUT NOW, AFTER LOSING THAT, SHE

00:15:30.878 --> 00:15:32.946
ISN’T EXACTLY SURE WHAT ROLE

00:15:32.946 --> 00:15:34.815
SHE SHOULD PLAY.

00:15:34.815 --> 00:15:36.383
&gt;&gt; OKAY!

00:15:36.383 --> 00:15:37.484
IN ORDER TO PROVE HOW

00:15:37.484 --> 00:15:39.286
BOOBIE-LICIOUS ANRI IS, LET’S

00:15:39.286 --> 00:15:41.253
GO HIT ON SOME HOTTIES.

00:15:41.253 --> 00:15:42.622
&gt;&gt; HOW DO YOU GET THAT?

00:15:42.622 --> 00:15:43.856
&gt;&gt; I HAVE TO HIT ON GIRLS?

00:15:43.856 --> 00:15:44.823
&gt;&gt; DON’T WORRY.

00:15:44.823 --> 00:15:46.358
I JUST WANNA USE YOU AS BAIT

00:15:46.358 --> 00:15:47.559
SO WHEN OTHER CHICKS SEE US,

00:15:47.559 --> 00:15:48.794
THEY THINK, "WELL IF THAT GIRL’S

00:15:48.794 --> 00:15:50.261
HANGING OUT WITH ’EM, I GUESS

00:15:50.261 --> 00:15:51.629
IT’S OKAY IF WE DO TOO."

00:15:51.629 --> 00:15:53.331
ALL YOU GOTTA DO IS STAND THERE.

00:15:53.331 --> 00:15:54.299
&gt;&gt; WAIT A SECOND, MASAOMI,

00:15:54.299 --> 00:15:54.899
YOU CAN’T--

00:15:54.899 --> 00:15:56.300
&gt;&gt; ALL RIGHT, GLAD YOU’RE ALL

00:15:56.300 --> 00:15:57.467
ON BOARD WITH THIS.

00:15:57.467 --> 00:15:58.903
ON YOUR MARK, GET SET, AND GO!

00:15:58.903 --> 00:15:59.803
HA HA!

00:15:59.803 --> 00:16:01.705
CATCH ME IF YOU CAN!

00:16:01.705 --> 00:16:02.939
&gt;&gt; DID HE JUST LEAVE?

00:16:02.939 --> 00:16:05.809
&gt;&gt; MASAOMI!

00:16:05.809 --> 00:16:06.709
[both sigh]

00:16:09.878 --> 00:16:11.747
&gt;&gt; IS IT OKAY WE DIDN’T GO

00:16:11.747 --> 00:16:12.514
WITH HIM?

00:16:12.514 --> 00:16:13.015
&gt;&gt; IT’S FINE.

00:16:13.015 --> 00:16:14.382
HE’S GONNA HIT ON GIRLS

00:16:14.382 --> 00:16:15.783
WHETHER WE’RE WITH HIM OR NOT.

00:16:15.783 --> 00:16:16.651
&gt;&gt; [giggles]

00:16:16.651 --> 00:16:17.919
&gt;&gt; OH, MAN.

00:16:17.919 --> 00:16:18.953
HMM?

00:16:18.953 --> 00:16:20.988
&gt;&gt; [giggles]

00:16:23.690 --> 00:16:25.492
&gt;&gt; HE’S HOPELESS.

00:16:25.492 --> 00:16:26.927
HE’S SO BAD WITH GIRLS,

00:16:26.927 --> 00:16:28.728
HE NEEDS A SERIOUS HANDICAP.

00:16:28.728 --> 00:16:31.864
HE’S LUCKY I’M SUCH A PIMP.

00:16:38.703 --> 00:16:43.407
[overlapping chatter]

00:16:44.775 --> 00:16:46.410
&gt;&gt; ’SCUSE ME.

00:16:51.614 --> 00:16:53.650
&gt;&gt; SHE KNEW WHAT WAS GOING ON.

00:16:53.650 --> 00:16:55.051
SHE REALIZED THAT BOTH THOSE

00:16:55.051 --> 00:16:56.819
BOYS WERE INTERESTED IN HER.

00:16:56.819 --> 00:16:59.588
BUT...

00:16:59.588 --> 00:17:01.890
&gt;&gt; HEY, THAT’S A PRETTY SUNSET.

00:17:01.890 --> 00:17:02.758
&gt;&gt; [gasps]

00:17:02.758 --> 00:17:03.458
&gt;&gt; OH!

00:17:03.458 --> 00:17:04.725
BUT THAT CLOUD OVER THERE

00:17:04.725 --> 00:17:05.793
DOESN’T LOOK GOOD.

00:17:05.793 --> 00:17:07.462
MAYBE IT’S GONNA RAIN LATER.

00:17:07.462 --> 00:17:09.564
WE PROBABLY SHOULD BE CAREFUL.

00:17:09.564 --> 00:17:11.265
&gt;&gt; YEAH.

00:17:16.703 --> 00:17:17.971
UM...

00:17:17.971 --> 00:17:19.572
&gt;&gt; UH, YEAH, WHAT IS IT?

00:17:19.572 --> 00:17:21.807
&gt;&gt; I SHOULD GO.

00:17:21.807 --> 00:17:22.875
GOOD-BYE.

00:17:22.875 --> 00:17:24.677
SEE YOU TOMORROW.

00:17:24.677 --> 00:17:25.811
&gt;&gt; OKAY.

00:17:25.811 --> 00:17:28.613
SEE YOU TOMORROW.

00:17:28.613 --> 00:17:30.848
[sighs]

00:17:30.848 --> 00:17:32.917
WHO SAYS "PRETTY SUNSET"?

00:17:32.917 --> 00:17:35.386
THAT WAS DUMB.

00:17:35.386 --> 00:17:37.020
&gt;&gt; IF EITHER OF THEM WERE TO ASK

00:17:37.020 --> 00:17:38.789
HER ON A DATE, SHE WOULDN’T KNOW

00:17:38.789 --> 00:17:39.890
WHAT TO SAY.

00:17:39.890 --> 00:17:41.591
IT WAS CONFUSING FOR HER.

00:17:41.591 --> 00:17:43.759
SHE STILL LOVED MIKA HARIMA.

00:17:43.759 --> 00:17:45.327
AND HER FEELINGS FOR THOSE

00:17:45.327 --> 00:17:46.796
TWO BOYS WERE THE SAME.

00:17:46.796 --> 00:17:47.930
SHE STILL DOESN’T

00:17:47.930 --> 00:17:48.797
UNDERSTAND THE DIFFERENCE

00:17:48.797 --> 00:17:53.534
BETWEEN FRIENDSHIP AND LOVE.

00:17:53.534 --> 00:17:56.437
WHAT DO THEY MEAN TO HER?

00:17:56.437 --> 00:17:59.740
MIKA, MIKADO, MASAOMI.

00:18:02.575 --> 00:18:03.910
&gt;&gt; SO YOU’RE NOT GONNA CHANGE

00:18:03.910 --> 00:18:04.777
YOUR MIND?

00:18:04.777 --> 00:18:05.778
&gt;&gt; C’MON, MAN, WE CAN’T DO

00:18:05.778 --> 00:18:06.913
ANYTHING WITHOUT YOU.

00:18:06.913 --> 00:18:08.915
&gt;&gt; I ALREADY TOLD YOU GUYS.

00:18:08.915 --> 00:18:10.816
THAT’S NOT WHO I AM ANYMORE.

00:18:10.816 --> 00:18:12.017
I WANT NOTHING TO DO WITH

00:18:12.017 --> 00:18:14.419
THAT NOW.

00:18:14.419 --> 00:18:16.621
I’M NOT COMIN’ BACK, OKAY?

00:18:16.621 --> 00:18:19.924
NOT TO THAT SIDE.

00:18:19.924 --> 00:18:23.894
&gt;&gt; SERIOUSLY?

00:18:24.894 --> 00:18:29.933
[siren]

00:18:58.090 --> 00:18:59.925
&gt;&gt; I SEE A LOT MORE PEOPLE

00:18:59.925 --> 00:19:00.792
AROUND THE CITY ARE

00:19:00.792 --> 00:19:01.993
WEARING YELLOW NOW.

00:19:01.993 --> 00:19:02.827
&gt;&gt; YELLOW?

00:19:02.827 --> 00:19:03.762
&gt;&gt; I KNOW.

00:19:03.762 --> 00:19:04.829
YOU NOTICE THEM MORE BECAUSE OF

00:19:04.829 --> 00:19:07.631
THEIR COLOR, UNLIKE THE DOLLARS.

00:19:07.631 --> 00:19:09.467
&gt;&gt; OH, THE YELLOW SCARVES,

00:19:09.467 --> 00:19:09.933
RIGHT?

00:19:09.933 --> 00:19:11.702
&gt;&gt; YOU KNOW THESE GUYS, SETTON?

00:19:11.702 --> 00:19:13.070
&gt;&gt; YEAH, I GUESS SO.

00:19:13.070 --> 00:19:14.637
I MEAN, THEY’VE BEEN AROUND

00:19:14.637 --> 00:19:15.772
A LONG TIME.

00:19:15.772 --> 00:19:17.774
&gt;&gt; WHAT’S THE YELLOW SCARVES?

00:19:17.774 --> 00:19:18.975
&gt;&gt; THEY WERE THIS GANG FROM

00:19:18.975 --> 00:19:20.176
IKEBUKURO.

00:19:20.176 --> 00:19:21.577
THEN THEY GOT IN A HUGE FIGHT

00:19:21.577 --> 00:19:22.511
WITH ANOTHER GANG AND KINDA

00:19:22.511 --> 00:19:24.045
FELL OFF THE MAP.

00:19:24.045 --> 00:19:26.181
&gt;&gt; OH, YEAH, I HAVE HEARD ABOUT

00:19:26.181 --> 00:19:28.416
THESE GUYS.

00:19:28.416 --> 00:19:29.617
&gt;&gt; SO DOES THAT MEAN

00:19:29.617 --> 00:19:30.585
THEY’RE BACK?

00:19:30.585 --> 00:19:31.852
&gt;&gt; IKEBUKURO’S GETTIN’ KINDA

00:19:31.852 --> 00:19:32.920
SKETCHY LATELY.

00:19:32.920 --> 00:19:33.988
&gt;&gt; YEAH.

00:19:33.988 --> 00:19:36.090
EVEN THE POLICE ARE SCARY THERE.

00:19:36.090 --> 00:19:37.591
I MEAN IT.

00:19:37.591 --> 00:19:38.992
DON’T MESS WITH THE COPS,

00:19:38.992 --> 00:19:40.159
ALL RIGHT?

00:19:40.159 --> 00:19:41.895
&gt;&gt; THE COPS?

00:19:41.895 --> 00:19:43.830
&gt;&gt; [groans]

00:19:43.830 --> 00:19:45.964
&gt;&gt; AH, LOOK, SHE FELL DOWN.

00:19:45.964 --> 00:19:46.832
LOSER.

00:19:46.832 --> 00:19:47.900
&gt;&gt; WE ONLY KICKED YOU A LITTLE

00:19:47.900 --> 00:19:48.667
BIT.

00:19:48.667 --> 00:19:49.935
DON’T BE SO CLUMSY.

00:19:49.935 --> 00:19:51.769
&gt;&gt; YOU’RE A LITTLE PARASITE.

00:19:51.769 --> 00:19:53.538
[laughter]

00:19:53.538 --> 00:19:54.806
&gt;&gt; DON’T YOU BE GIVIN’ ME

00:19:54.806 --> 00:19:56.007
THAT STINK-EYE.

00:19:56.007 --> 00:19:57.074
&gt;&gt; IT’LL BE A WHILE BEFORE THEY

00:19:57.074 --> 00:19:59.176
SOLVE THAT SLASHER CASE.

00:19:59.176 --> 00:20:01.011
&gt;&gt; HEY, DID YOU GUYS HEAR?

00:20:01.011 --> 00:20:02.613
EVERYBODY SAYIN’ THAT THE

00:20:02.613 --> 00:20:03.747
DOLLARS ARE ACTUALLY THE

00:20:03.747 --> 00:20:04.647
SLASHER.

00:20:04.647 --> 00:20:05.748
SOME SAY THEY’RE THE BLACK

00:20:05.748 --> 00:20:06.816
RIDER, TOO.

00:20:06.816 --> 00:20:08.584
&gt;&gt; HUH? WHO SAID THAT?

00:20:08.584 --> 00:20:10.219
&gt;&gt; I DON’T THINK THAT’S TRUE.

00:20:10.219 --> 00:20:12.487
&gt;&gt; ALL JOKING ASIDE, YOU

00:20:12.487 --> 00:20:13.955
SHOULD REALLY WATCH OUT FOR THE

00:20:13.955 --> 00:20:15.457
YELLOW SCARVES.

00:20:15.457 --> 00:20:16.958
SOME OF THOSE GUYS REALLY DON’T

00:20:16.958 --> 00:20:18.159
LIKE THE DOLLARS.

00:20:18.159 --> 00:20:19.828
THEY’RE KINDA PISSED ABOUT HOW

00:20:19.828 --> 00:20:20.728
BIG THEY’VE GOTTEN WHILE

00:20:20.728 --> 00:20:21.962
THEY’VE LAID LOW.

00:20:21.962 --> 00:20:23.797
